author: rwesten
msg: STANBOL-1245: commons.marmotta.kiwi is an OSGI Bundle for the Marmotta Kiwi Triplestore that also provides a OSGI Component to configure Kiwi TripleStore instances. The launchers.bundlelists.marmotta.kiwi module provides a bundlelist with all the dependencies required for the Kiwi Triplestore. Dependencies for some supported DBs and Caching options are commented

author: rwesten
